<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 16:07:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登政府采取行动遏制企业贪婪，美国信用卡持有人将得到救济</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/relief-for-credit-card-holders-in-us-as-biden-admin-moves-to-check-corporate-greed/articleshow/108243716.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108243716.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 15:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/relief-for-credit-card-holders-in-us-as-biden-admin-moves-to-check-corporate-greed/articleshow/108243716.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国设定了5%左右的经济增长目标，但承认实现起来并不容易</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-sets-an-economic-growth-target-of-around-5-but-acknowledges-it-will-not-be-easy-to-achieve/articleshow/108238278.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108238278.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:25:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-sets-an-economic-growth-target-of-around-5-but-acknowledges-it-will-not-be-easy-to-achieve/articleshow/108238278.cms</guid></item><item><title>“比9/11更糟糕”：马斯克攻击拜登“非法移民”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/worse-than-9/11-musk-attacks-biden-over-illegal-immigrants/articleshow/108241115.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108241115.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃隆·马斯克对拜登政府运送非法移民进入美国的秘密航班造成的国家安全漏洞表示担忧，暗示潜在威胁比 9/11 更严重。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:48:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/worse-than-9/11-musk-attacks-biden-over-illegal-immigrants/articleshow/108241115.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国将音频泄露归咎于“个人错误”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-blames-individual-error-for-leaked-audio-military-personnel/articleshow/108237347.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108237347.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国淡化了泄露的涉及高级军事人员讨论乌克兰冲突的录音，并将其归因于个人错误。柏林强调与盟友的持续信任。这次拦截是由于新加坡航展期间未经授权的连接而发生的。德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨对授权向乌克兰运送金牛座导弹持谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:51:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-blames-individual-error-for-leaked-audio-military-personnel/articleshow/108237347.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争：印度在联合国大会上表示，只有两国解决方案才能实现持久和平</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/israel-hamas-war-only-two-state-solution-will-deliver-enduring-peace-india-says-at-unga/articleshow/108219564.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108219564.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度的鲁奇拉·坎博伊在联合国谴责加沙冲突，敦促两国解决方案并立即缓和局势。她要求释放人质并呼吁增加人道主义援助。印度致力于通过直接谈判支持巴勒斯坦独立，确保边界安全和持久和平。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/israel-hamas-war-only-two-state-solution-will-deliver-enduring-peace-india-says-at-unga/articleshow/108219564.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦新总理谢巴兹·谢里夫下令与国际货币基金组织“立即”举行会谈，为陷入困境的经济提供延期贷款</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/new-pakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharif-orders-immediate-talks-with-imf-for-extended-facility-for-ailing-economy/articleshow/108237768.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108237768.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦新总理谢赫巴兹·谢里夫已下令与国际货币基金组织“立即”进行谈判，为资金短缺的国家提供延期基金安排，并表示改善经济状况将是已获得“授权”的巴基斯坦政府的首要任务。今年 1 月，巴基斯坦根据去年 6 月达成的现有 30 亿美元备用安排（SBA）从国际货币基金组织（IMF）获得了超过 7 亿美元的第二笔资金，当时巴基斯坦正在慢慢走向违约。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:17:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/new-pakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharif-orders-immediate-talks-with-imf-for-extended-facility-for-ailing-economy/articleshow/108237768.cms</guid></item><item><title>超级星期二：拜登、特朗普在美国大选中的重要日子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/americas-massive-multi-state-voting-event-super-tuesday-a-big-day-for-joe-biden-donald-trump-in-us-presidential-elections/photostory/108229813.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108229813.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/americas-massive-multi-state-voting-event-super-tuesday-a-big-day-for-joe-biden-donald-trump-in-us-presidential-elections/photostory/108229813.cms</guid></item><item><title>肯尼亚警方称内罗毕国家公园上空飞机相撞造成2人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/2-killed-in-midair-plane-collision-above-nairobi-national-park-kenya-police-say/articleshow/108236574.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108236574.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/2-killed-in-midair-plane-collision-above-nairobi-national-park-kenya-police-say/articleshow/108236574.cms</guid></item><item><title>在阿根廷的贫民窟，贫困加剧困扰着哈维尔·米雷的紧缩政策</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/in-argentinas-barrios-rising-poverty-stalks-javier-mileis-austerity-drive/articleshow/108235754.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108235754.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;黛博拉·布兰科 (Debora Blanco) 与阿根廷贫困人口不断上涨的食品价格作斗争。反对总统米莱紧缩措施的抗议活动日益增多。非政府组织报告粮食援助减少。 Milei 的目标是实现财政平衡，但透明度和社会动荡带来了挑战。社会安全网削弱，导致长期贫困。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:15:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/in-argentinas-barrios-rising-poverty-stalks-javier-mileis-austerity-drive/articleshow/108235754.cms</guid></item><item><title>加纳总统推迟就反 LGBTQ 法做出决定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ghana-president-delays-decision-on-anti-lgbtq-law/articleshow/108235580.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108235580.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加纳总统表示，在最高法院对法律挑战做出裁决之前，他不会决定是否将一项有争议的反 LGBTQ 法案签署为法律。他说，一名公民已向最高法院提出质疑，并宣称他将“在采取任何行动之前等待法院的裁决”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ghana-president-delays-decision-on-anti-lgbtq-law/articleshow/108235580.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本首相将于 4 月 11 日向美国国会发表讲话</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-pm-to-address-us-congress-on-april-11/articleshow/108235350.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108235350.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本首相岸田文雄将于4月11日在美国国会发表讲话，深化两国外交关系。此次访问可能涉及讨论日本在 AUKUS 安全伙伴关系下的防务技术合作。岸田的访问是在戴维营与拜登和韩国总理举行具有里程碑意义的峰会之后进行的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:03:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-pm-to-address-us-congress-on-april-11/articleshow/108235350.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其拘留七名涉嫌向以色列摩萨德出售信息的人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-detains-seven-suspected-of-selling-information-to-israels-mossad/articleshow/108235092.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108235092.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;土耳其警方拘留了 7 名涉嫌向摩萨德出售信息的人，其中包括私家侦探。在贝尔格莱德接受培训的侦探收到了加密货币付款。哈马斯冲突导致土耳其和以色列关系紧张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:58:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-detains-seven-suspected-of-selling-information-to-israels-mossad/articleshow/108235092.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着地区争端升温，中国增加国防开支</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-boosts-defence-spending-as-regional-disputes-heat-up/articleshow/108230162.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108230162.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据列出政府未来一年财务计划的预算报告，中国到 2024 年将在国防上支出 1.665 万亿元人民币（合 2314 亿美元）。尽管中国人民解放军在人员数量上超过了美军，但它的国防预算位居世界第二，仅次于美国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:45:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-boosts-defence-spending-as-regional-disputes-heat-up/articleshow/108230162.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰称乌克兰海上无人机在克里米亚附近损坏了俄罗斯黑海舰队巡逻船</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-sea-drones-damage-russian-black-sea-fleet-patrol-ship-near-crimea-ukraine-says/articleshow/108228817.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108228817.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰海上无人机在刻赤海峡附近击毁了俄罗斯黑海舰队巡逻舰谢尔盖·科托夫号，造成其船尾、右舷和左舷受损。这艘价值约 6500 万美元的船暂时停止了火车和公路交通。乌克兰军方此前使用海军无人机在克里米亚附近摧毁了一艘俄罗斯登陆舰。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:04:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-sea-drones-damage-russian-black-sea-fleet-patrol-ship-near-crimea-ukraine-says/articleshow/108228817.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯-乌克兰战争：为何泄露的德国军事录音引起强烈抗议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-ukraine-war-why-a-leaked-german-military-recording-is-causing-outcry/articleshow/108224169.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108224169.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一段 38 分钟的录音被泄露，其中德国高级军事官员讨论了为乌克兰提供军事支持以对抗俄罗斯入侵的可能性。德国政府强烈否认有关泄露的谈话表明柏林正在准备对俄罗斯开战的指控。通话录音包括德国空军参谋长英戈·格哈茨和其他德国空军官员就后勤问题进行的讨论。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 05:03:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-ukraine-war-why-a-leaked-german-military-recording-is-causing-outcry/articleshow/108224169.cms</guid></item><item><title>海地犯罪团伙试图在对主要政府场所的最新袭击中夺取主要机场的控制权</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gangs-in-haiti-try-to-seize-control-of-main-airport-in-newest-attack-on-key-government-sites/articleshow/108222334.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108222334.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;全副武装的团伙试图夺取海地主要国际机场的控制权，并与警察和士兵交火。他们占领了两座最大的监狱，释放了数千名囚犯。已实施夜间宵禁。美国大使馆敦促美国公民离开海地。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gangs-in-haiti-try-to-seize-control-of-main-airport-in-newest-attack-on-key-government-sites/articleshow/108222334.cms</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾海岸警卫队称船只与中国船只相撞受损</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippine-coast-guard-says-ship-damaged-in-collision-with-chinese-vessel/articleshow/108222107.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108222107.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;菲律宾海岸警卫队表示，周二，其一艘船只在南海一个偏远前哨基地向菲律宾军队执行补给任务时与一艘中国海岸警卫队船只相撞，造成损坏。菲律宾海岸警卫队准将杰伊·塔里拉(Jay Tarriela)在社交媒体平台上发帖称，中国海警和其他船只进行了“危险的机动和拦截”，导致碰撞，导致“菲律宾海岸警卫队(PCG)船只受到轻微结构性损坏”。 X。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippine-coast-guard-says-ship-damaged-in-collision-with-chinese-vessel/articleshow/108222107.cms</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装部长表示，进入也门水域的船只必须获得许可</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ships-entering-yemeni-waters-must-obtain-permit-houthi-minister-says/articleshow/108221911.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108221911.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;胡塞武装海事管理局要求船只进入也门水域获得许可证。胡塞武装分子袭击国际航运以声援巴勒斯坦人。美国和英国以爆炸回应。也门的命令影响了曼德海峡的领海，这对全球航运至关重要。也门冲突自 2014 年以来一直持续。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:48:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ships-entering-yemeni-waters-must-obtain-permit-houthi-minister-says/articleshow/108221911.cms</guid></item><item><title>平壤警告美韩演习后果</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pyongyang-warns-of-consequences-over-us-south-korea-drills/articleshow/108221936.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108221936.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜周二表示，首尔和华盛顿将为本周开始的大规模军事演习付出“高昂代价”，并敦促盟国停止“疯狂的战争演习”。华盛顿和首尔表示，华盛顿和首尔周一开始举行年度春季军事演习，参加演习的部队人数比 2023 年增加了一倍，以加强应对平壤不断升级的核威胁的准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pyongyang-warns-of-consequences-over-us-south-korea-drills/articleshow/108221936.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚推定总统普拉博沃承诺“非常顺利”的权力过渡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesias-presumed-president-prabowo-promises-very-smooth-transition-of-power/articleshow/108221619.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108221619.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;普拉博沃·苏比安托承诺平稳权力交接，延续维多多的政策，目标是实现 8% 的经济增长。寻求私有化、提高税率、创造就业机会、粮食自给自足、投资、财政纪律。考虑投票率、粮食出口、民主、佐科的支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesias-presumed-president-prabowo-promises-very-smooth-transition-of-power/articleshow/108221619.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>